			p.big Linux is <i>Free/Libre and Open Source Software</i>. Unlike Windows and macOS, whose sole purpose is to make a profit off you, Linux wants to create the best possible experience for its users. Linux allows you to examine what it does and how it is done, so you can sleep easy knowing that your computer is not spying on you in any way. If you disagree with a feature, you can even modify it to suit your needs.
			p.big Plus, Linux is free, now and always. And you'll get all future updates, no matter how old your computer is.
